Package com.kanbine.backend.dto.request

package com.kanbine.backend.dto.request
This package contains Data Transfer Objects (DTOs) for handling requests in the Kanbine backend application. These DTOs are used to encapsulate data sent to the API for creating or updating resources.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AssignmentRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an assignment creation or update request.
    TimeCardRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a time card creation or update request.
    UserRequest
    Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a user creation or update request.
